months before he started
working on the rest of the film.

1655
01:39:52,194 --> 01:39:54,779
And I played it while we were shooting.

1656
01:39:55,030 --> 01:39:57,740
It really created the mood
inside the church

1657
01:39:57,825 --> 01:40:00,743
and helped the actors
come up with their performances.

1658
01:40:01,745 --> 01:40:03,538
Diane said that
with that piece of music,

1659
