(LAUGHING)

1747
01:46:14,451 --> 01:46:18,245
The water here is a sort of baptism
as it washes her feet.

1748
01:46:19,289 --> 01:46:22,792
The look on her face seems
somehow transcendent.

1749
01:46:23,335 --> 01:46:25,961
Someone once told her
that one day she'd be happy again,

1750
01:46:26,046 --> 01:46:29,215
